text: Beygulovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Shemyaksky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 172 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 55 km from Ufa, 5 km from Oktyabrsky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Beygulovo
